reviewText: The virgin Suicides was beautiful and so was American Beauty in a more blunt sort of way. Both were great.

reviewText: American Beauty is a classic with great acting and music. Visually entertaining as well. The Virgin Suicides is a great story with the same- great acting, music. Love them both, so it was fantastic to find them together.
